     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "Fruit()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Wow! We now have a fruit class. It can't do anything, but it certainly is a class and we certainly have instantiated it."
   ]
  },
